data.description: Walk into Instant Equity!!! House appraised for $370k in August 2023. This charming 3 bedroom 1 bath bungalow is a fixer-upper with great potential for investors and homebuyers who are willing to roll up their sleeves and bring their vision to life. With a little TLC, this property can be transformed into a cozy and inviting home that suits your lifestyle. Inside, you'll find a kitchen, three bedrooms and 1 full bathroom that await your personal touch. Property features a long driveway that can accommodate at least 6 vehicles. The property sits on a large lot that offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities and entertainment. Major mechanicals updated water heater (2016), roof (2017) and newer kitchen appliances. Located near Dick's Sporting Goods Park, Northfield Shopping Center and Rocky Mountain Arsenal National Wildlife Refuge.  Easy Access to Public Transportation & to the greater Denver area.
